Milestone birthdays are the perfect opportunity to give a giant birthday card; especially one with a unique photo collage filled with pictures of friends and family. The template is set up for you to add your own photos, so they will automatically form a neat number 40. Inside there is another big 40 and the words "cheers to 40 years" as well as a Happy 40th Birthday message, which you can also personalize.This custom photo collage contains a mixture of portrait, square and landscape shapes to give you lots of flexibility for placement of your photos.
